==Infrastrutura==
===Trasport===

====Stredes====
Berlin's transport infrastructure is highly complex, providing a diverse range of urban mobility.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.businesslocationcenter.de/en/business-location/business-location/infrastructure/transport-infrastructure/passenger-and-freight-service |title=Mobile capital |publisher=Business Location Center |date=2011 |access-date=14 February 2016 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414050459/https://www.businesslocationcenter.de/en/business-location/business-location/infrastructure/transport-infrastructure/passenger-and-freight-service |archive-date=14 April 2016}}</ref> A total of 979 bridges cross {{cvt|197|km|0}} of inner-city waterways. {{cvt|5422|km|0}} of roads run through Berlin, of which {{cvt|77|km|0}} are motorways ({{lang|de|[[Autobahn]]}}).<ref name="statistics"/> In 2013, 1.344&nbsp;million motor vehicles were registered in the city.<ref name="statistics">{{cite web |url=https://www.statistik-berlin-brandenburg.de/BasisZeitreiheGrafik/Bas-Strassenverkehr.asp?Ptyp=300&Sageb=46002&creg=BBB&anzwer=6 |title=Straßenverkehr 2013 |website=Amt für Statistik Berlin Brandenburg |access-date=28 March 2015 |language=de |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402133316/https://www.statistik-berlin-brandenburg.de/BasisZeitreiheGrafik/Bas-Strassenverkehr.asp?Ptyp=300&Sageb=46002&creg=BBB&anzwer=6 |archive-date=2 April 2015 |url-status=dead}}</ref> With 377 cars per 1000 residents in 2013 (570/1000 in Germany), Berlin as a Western global city has one of the lowest numbers of cars per capita.{{citation needed|date=January 2021}} In 2012, around 7,600 mostly beige colored [[taxicab]]s were in service.{{citation needed|date=January 2021}} Since 2011, a number of app based [[electric vehicle|e-car]] and [[electric motorcycles and scooters|e-scooter]] sharing services have evolved.

====Ferata====
[[File:Berlin Hauptbahnhof0514.JPG|thumb|{{lang|de|[[Berlin Hauptbahnhof]]|italic=no}} ie la majera [[stazion dla ferata]] a partimënc de l'Europa.]]

Linies de ferata a distanza culeghea Berlin cun duta la majera ziteies de la Germania y cun n grum de ziteies di stac Europeics che cunfina. Linies regioneles dl {{lang|de|[[Verkehrsverbund Berlin-Brandenburg]]}} pieta servijes ai raions dl Brandenburg ntëurvia y al [[Mer Baltich]]. L {{lang|de|[[Berlin Hauptbahnhof]]|italic=no}} ie la majera [[stazion dla ferata]] a partimënc de l'Europa.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://berliner-hbf.de/bahnhof_berlin_hbf_daten_und_fakten.html |title=Bahnhof Berlin Hbf Daten und Fakten |publisher=[[Berlin Hauptbahnhof]] |access-date=14 February 2016 |language=de |archive-date=15 January 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160115155518/https://berliner-hbf.de/bahnhof_berlin_hbf_daten_und_fakten.html |url-status=dead }}</ref> {{lang|de|[[Deutsche Bahn]]|italic=no}} runs high speed [[Intercity-Express]] trains to domestic destinations like {{lang|de|[[Hamburg]]|italic=no}}, [[Munich]], [[Cologne]], {{lang|de|[[Stuttgart]]|italic=no}}, {{lang|de|[[Frankfurt am Main]]|italic=no}} and others. It also runs an airport express rail service, as well as trains to several international destinations like [[Viena]], Praga, {{lang|de|[[Zürich]]|italic=no}}, [[Varsavia]], [[Breslau]], [[Budapest]] y [[Amsterdam]].

====Trasport sun ega====

Berlin is connected to the [[Elbe]] and [[Oder]] rivers via the [[Spree (river)|Spree]] and the [[Havel]] rivers. There are no frequent passenger connections to and from Berlin by water, but some of the freight is transported via waterways. Berlin's largest harbour, the [[Westhafen]], is located in the district of [[Moabit]]. It is a transhipment and storage site for inland shipping with a growing importance.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.morgenpost.de/bezirke/mitte/article231791147/Wie-der-Westhafen-Berlins-Gueterverkehr-in-die-Zukunft-bringt.html |title=Wie der Westhafen Berlins Güterverkehr in die Zukunft bringt |website=morgenpost.de |date=14 March 2021 |accessdate=4 September 2021 |language=German |archive-date=4 September 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210904114311/https://www.morgenpost.de/bezirke/mitte/article231791147/Wie-der-Westhafen-Berlins-Gueterverkehr-in-die-Zukunft-bringt.html |url-status=live }}</ref>

====Curieres danter ziteies====
